/span></p><p>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggW5ReZhLFf_label","label":"ggW5ReZhLFf_label","default":"<p>CHECK AVAILABILITY&gt;&gt;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggp7UicNiHR_text","label":"ggp7UicNiHR_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><strong>Manifestation isn’t a myth. It’s not wishful thinking. It’s a measurable alignment. It’s your current. And right now, you have the opportunity to switch it back on.</strong></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p>"}],
